time. Palcohol is made to be dissolved in
water, but it could ALSO be snorted -- which

00:02:48.180 --> 00:02:52.180
is the worry for some legislators though there
doesn't seem to be much evidence that anyone

00:02:52.180 --> 00:02:56.430
other than one VICE reporter actually did
it. The reason snorting it would make sense,

00:02:56.430 --> 00:02:59.810
from a drunks perspective, is because you
wouldn't have to wait the few minutes for

00:02:59.810 --> 00:03:03.849
the alcohol to hit the stomach, and then small
intestine. The blood vessels in the nose are

00:03:03.849 --> 00:03:11.459
close to the skin, and if the ethanol is absorbable
